12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 85.58B, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 85.58B. A. The Risk Management Administrator, pursuant
16 to the provisions of this section and Section 85.34 of this title,
17 may obtain or provide insurance coverage for any vehicle, vessel or
18 aircraft used for or in fire fighting firefighting or services
19 provided by the districts, departments and services specified in
20 subsection D of this section and may obtain or provide indemnity
21 coverage for any board member, official, employee or volunteer of
22 any entity specified in subsection D of this section for any errors
23 and omissions or liability risks arising from the performance of
24 their official duties pursuant to law.
